  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要梳理一下评论的生命周期状态机。核心流程是：用户创建评论后先进入待审核状态，审核通过就公开可见，被拒绝则隐藏，当然也可以直接删除。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Pending",
        "Approved",
        "Rejected",
        "Deleted",
        "[*]"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，我理解为起点是创建评论进入Pending，然后可以Approve到Approved状态，Reject到Rejected状态，或者Delete直接到Deleted。Deleted应该是终态吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Pending",
        "Approved",
        "Rejected",
        "Deleted",
        "Create Comment",
        "Approve",
        "Reject",
        "Delete"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Deleted是终态。另外Approved和Rejected状态下也都可以Delete。还有，Pending本身是个复合状态，里面包含AwaitingModeration这个子状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Deleted",
        "Approved",
        "Rejected",
        "Pending",
        "AwaitingModeration"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "好的，那Approved和Rejected内部结构呢？需要细化吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Approved",
        "Rejected"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Approved里面分Visible和Edited，评论发布后可见，用户可以编辑，编辑完回到Visible。Rejected里面分Hidden和WithReason，隐藏后可以补充拒绝原因。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Approved",
        "Visible",
        "Edited",
        "Rejected",
        "Hidden",
        "WithReason",
        "Update",
        "Add Rejection Reason"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "结构清楚了，我来画一下。Pending、Approved、Rejected都作为复合状态，内部包含对应的子状态流转。右侧加上注释说明每个主状态的含义。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Pending",
        "Approved",
        "Rejected",
        "Deleted",
        "notes"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
